{"tid":2326373,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"親政府的士司機 去年元朗揮酒樽襲政見不同市民 獲准守行為了事 婦人卻被控暴動","createTime":"2020-12-15T09:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T12:01:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3e0c2c004ca1c4f4c0c0eed38d17a9884f6c8c","tid":2326373,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iMGCPnAD6Vh_IzBUc553VCPzov4=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LMI2WEWF7JGRFMCT2MIZXD4EEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiMGCPnAD6Vh_IzBUc553VCPzov4%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLMI2WEWF7JGRFMCT2MIZXD4EEQ.jpg&h=1d6a7e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民去年9月在元朗舉行7.21白衣人恐襲兩個月紀念集會。翌日凌晨，有醉酒的士司機因政見問題與他人爭執，並多次揮動玻璃樽意圖施襲，最後遭圍毆私了。司機原被控兩項普通襲擊罪，案件今再訊，控方鑑於司機無傷及任何人，反而他本人卻嚴重受傷，決定以守行為了事。裁判官頒令被告以1,000元簽保守行為一年，撤回控罪；至於涉嫌私了司機的女子早前被控暴動等罪，案件將於區院審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/7TTHV5YDIVERVPSLF7BAYIGY4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2F7TTHV5YDIVERVPSLF7BAYIGY4E%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=d747288a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2F7TTHV5YDIVERVPSLF7BAYIGY4E%2F&h=b2f076a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/7TTHV5YDIVERVPSLF7BAYIGY4E/</a>"},{"pid":"acfa9560c050eca570b08dfaa41c462990e5a555","tid":2326373,"uid":183844,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾律政司"},{"pid":"2eacc9add7c4e62361b94164c199b1cfaa30eec7","tid":2326373,"uid":46275,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"法律面前，人人平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\